<item>
            <title>[SYNAPSE-824] Can&apos;t configure a socket time out for server and client side seperatly. </title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SYNAPSE-824</link>
                <project id="12310201" key="SYNAPSE">Synapse</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When we set the Socket timeout in nhttp.properties it will be set for both server and client sides. But we should be able to configure separately. &lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>any</environment>
